  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of surgical excision of cardiophrenic lymph nodes in patients with advanced
      ovarian cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The role of cardiophrenic lymph node assessment and excision in advanced ovarian cancer is
      still debatable , correlation of radiological finding with pathological findings after
      reaction of radiological positive lymph nodes and its impact in diseases free survival and
      over all survival
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
